    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方块碰碰是一款本地多人（最多4人）的派对游戏。你需要操作自己的角色碰碰搬运方块像堆积木一样码方块来达成游戏目标，率先达成目标的一方将取得游戏的胜利。游戏里的方块有多种类型，造型各异，重量各不相同，有些特殊方块还有一些功能性。游戏画风轻松简洁，氛围愉快，适合与朋友一同游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：可爱的可操作角色<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321690/extras/213eda4abec94353891b5ea7fa6226cd.avif?t=1732585524\" width=724 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造型各异功能独特的积木方块：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321690/extras/41194576d4abaf17f237902cc8b32151.avif?t=1732585524\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321690/extras_big/41194576d4abaf17f237902cc8b32151.avif?t=1732585524 width=800 height=592 /></span></p>",
